# Kristoffer K.'s Web Developer Portfolio

A modern, responsive portfolio website built with Next.js and Tailwind CSS to showcase my web development projects and skills.

![Portfolio Screenshot](public/images/portfolio-screenshot.jpg)

## üöÄ Features

- Modern and clean UI design
- Responsive for all device sizes
- Dark mode support
- Interactive project showcase
- Contact form with EmailJS integration
- SEO optimized
- Fast loading performance

## üíª Technologies Used

- **Frontend**: Next.js, React, TypeScript
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS
